{
  "stem": "942.4",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when these fellows were caught, they were hanged right away, in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I remember the first time when I came in from the work detail, and there was this fellow hanging inside the gate, and that was a shock to see it.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And with a big plaque here-- this is what happens to people that run away, you know.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And after that, I've seen many times people that were trying to steal some food from the kitchen, and they were caught.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At appell, you know, when we were being counted, you know, at, at night, when all these 40,000 people were standing, this guy was brought in front there.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he was tied up on a drum, sort of, like he was bent over.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "His hands were tied down and his feet.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And this fellow was a huge guy.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he came, and he gave him 25 lashes.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And once you got 25 lashes, that was your end, you know.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You'd never survive that anymore.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we had to all watch this type of things and you know, other things.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I was separate from my-- you know, I was on a separate detail.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Other details I was working on, we had to carry these cement and steel pylons that were used around for electrified fences.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Three of us had to carry this, you know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was a-- you know, this square cement pole, you know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it was sort of bent at the end, you know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I don't know how heavy this was, but three of us had to carry this.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And you know, it was sitting on my shoulder, on the bones.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I thought that this will surely kill me, you know.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
